OL,3,CHaygrove School to be rebuilt at new
OL,4,Csite after being found 'unsafe'
OL,6,FA school in Somerset that was deemed
OL,7,Funsafe at the start of the academic
OL,8,Fyear will be entirely rebuilt at a
OL,9,Fnew site.
OL,11,FHaygrove School in Bridgwater was
OL,12,Ftold it could no longer use its main
OL,13,Fbuilding in September after the
OL,14,FGovernment discovered it had "issues
OL,15,Fwith structural integrity."
OL,17,FCaledonian Modular, which constructed
OL,18,Fthe building, went out of business in
OL,19,F2022, prompting the Department for
OL,20,FEducation to check the safety of
OL,21,FHaygrove and several other schools.
